00:00:08.204 --> 00:00:12.973 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Narrator) In a betrayal of epic</i>
 <i>proportions, Squad Four hunts</i>
 <i>down Akari and Michelle,</i>

00:00:13.006 --> 00:00:18.410 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>as test specimens. And while a</i>
 <i>multinational crew unites to</i>
 <i>signal Earth for help,</i>

00:00:18.444 --> 00:00:20.245 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>the terraformars strike.</i>

00:00:21.879 --> 00:00:26.148 position:19% line:77% align:start
 <i>Sparks fly between the</i>
 <i>terraformars, survivors, and</i>
 <i>traitorous Squad Four.</i>

00:00:26.181 --> 00:00:31.152 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>Meanwhile, the ruthless Bao has</i>
 <i>succeeded in capturing Akari and</i>
 <i>Michelle.</i>

00:00:31.185 --> 00:00:35.855 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>Thanks to him, Yaeko finds</i>
 <i>herself in the middle of a swarm</i>
 <i>of terraformars,</i>

00:00:35.888 --> 00:00:40.090 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>and the badly injured Alex can't</i>
 <i>help but scramble to her rescue.</i>

00:00:40.124 --> 00:00:43.259 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Now, as dread seems to push out</i>
 <i>all hope,</i>

00:00:43.293 --> 00:00:47.895 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Joseph, the leader of Squad Six,</i>
 <i>arrives with a curious flourish.</i>

00:00:48.196 --> 00:00:50.097 position:21% line:89% align:start
What? How did? What?

00:00:51.764 --> 00:00:53.366 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't you worry.

00:00:54.267 --> 00:00:57.402 position:7% line:83% align:start
Your passion and elegant love
called loud and clear.

00:02:45.804 --> 00:02:49.141 position:27% line:89% align:start
Alex is gone. And Yaeko!

00:02:50.041 --> 00:02:51.808 position:21% line:89% align:start
Where are you, Joe?

00:02:52.210 --> 00:02:54.177 position:13% line:89% align:start
What's taking you so long?

00:02:54.211 --> 00:02:55.178 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:02:58.913 --> 00:03:01.114 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) We need you.</i>

00:03:04.817 --> 00:03:06.485 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm here now.

00:03:07.219 --> 00:03:09.086 position:5% line:89% align:start
Where are...?

00:03:09.554 --> 00:03:11.988 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>Where are this guy's clothes?</i>

00:03:12.289 --> 00:03:19.926 position:13% line:77% align:start
[Pained Groan] <i>Hold on, he</i>
 <i>hasn't mutated yet. That's his</i>
 <i>natural body?</i>

00:03:22.295 --> 00:03:24.530 position:24% line:89% align:start
Now then. [Grunts]

00:03:24.563 --> 00:03:28.099 position:10% line:83% align:start
W-w-w-w-wait wait wait. Just
slow down now.

00:03:28.132 --> 00:03:31.468 position:13% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Yaeko) Is he a sex maniac</i>
 <i>with rippling abs?</i>

00:03:31.501 --> 00:03:35.003 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Panicked Sounds]

00:03:35.036 --> 00:03:36.238 position:69% line:89% align:start
Found it.

00:03:36.271 --> 00:03:37.038 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:03:38.405 --> 00:03:41.808 position:10% line:83% align:start
I have one syringe of avian
serum left.

00:03:42.041 --> 00:03:44.076 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Joseph) He is an avian, isn't</i>
 <i>he?</i>

00:03:44.109 --> 00:03:46.277 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's right.

00:03:46.310 --> 00:03:50.813 position:19% line:77% align:start
Hurry. Every second counts.
There's a 50/50 chance he'll
make a full recovery.

00:03:50.846 --> 00:03:53.881 position:21% line:89% align:start
Okay. [Pained Noise]

00:03:57.017 --> 00:03:58.118 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Exhales]

00:03:58.151 --> 00:03:59.852 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Chuckles]

00:04:01.053 --> 00:04:02.321 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Exhales]

00:04:07.057 --> 00:04:10.093 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Groans]

00:04:12.995 --> 00:04:15.930 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>This is the Roman Federation</i>
 <i>guy...</i>

00:04:15.963 --> 00:04:18.365 position:16% line:5% align:start
 <i>The leader of Squad Six.</i>

00:04:18.565 --> 00:04:21.300 position:19% line:5% align:start
 <i>What's he doing here?</i>

00:04:22.368 --> 00:04:23.368 position:44% line:89% align:start
Joo.

00:04:23.401 --> 00:04:27.837 position:21% line:89% align:start
[All] Joo, jo, joo.

00:04:32.974 --> 00:04:34.609 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Yaeko) They're coming!</i>

00:04:34.643 --> 00:04:35.908 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'll take care of them.

00:04:35.942 --> 00:04:36.809 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Gasps]

00:04:37.844 --> 00:04:39.379 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Yaeko) You'll take care of</i>
 <i>them?</i>

00:04:41.113 --> 00:04:43.114 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Yaeko) You mean you're gonna</i>
 <i>fight all these terraformars,</i>
 <i>alone?</i>

00:04:43.147 --> 00:04:45.549 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Yaeko) Wait, what are you</i>
 <i>doing? Are you meditating?</i>

00:04:45.583 --> 00:04:48.350 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Inhales]

00:04:49.051 --> 00:04:50.486 position:5% line:89% align:start
Snap out of it!

00:04:51.052 --> 00:04:52.220 position:44% line:89% align:start
Kay.

00:04:52.253 --> 00:04:53.020 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hmph!

00:04:54.388 --> 00:04:56.456 position:30% line:89% align:start
Come get some!

00:04:58.457 --> 00:04:59.958 position:24% line:89% align:start
Who wants to die?

00:05:02.059 --> 00:05:04.395 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Gasps]

00:05:10.465 --> 00:05:14.034 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Grunting]

00:05:14.467 --> 00:05:16.035 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Exhales]

00:05:17.369 --> 00:05:21.306 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Yaeko) I remember something</i>
 <i>Michelle once said.</i>

00:05:25.908 --> 00:05:26.875 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Joe?</i>

00:05:28.243 --> 00:05:32.912 position:10% line:77% align:start
Oh, yeah, Joe. The track and
field star. I first saw him on
TV.

00:05:34.280 --> 00:05:37.948 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) In his junior year of</i>
 <i>high school, at the age of 17,</i>

00:05:37.982 --> 00:05:41.017 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>he won the gold medal in the</i>
 <i>world decathlon.</i>

00:05:41.619 --> 00:05:45.287 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>People called him the "King of</i>
 <i>Athletes."</i>

00:05:46.388 --> 00:05:49.223 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) But that's not the</i>
 <i>whole story.</i>

00:05:49.257 --> 00:05:52.159 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>After graduating, he quit track</i>
 <i>and field.</i>

00:05:52.192 --> 00:05:58.162 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>He studied for exams, got high</i>
 <i>marks, and earned a spot in the</i>
 <i>EU's top university.</i>

00:05:58.196 --> 00:06:03.499 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>He then attended an elite air</i>
 <i>force academy, and graduated </i>
 <i>at the top of his class.</i>

00:06:03.533 --> 00:06:06.101 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Earning him an air force</i>
 <i>officer's rank,</i>

00:06:06.134 --> 00:06:09.270 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>and master's degrees in biology</i>
 <i>and aeronautics.</i>

00:06:09.470 --> 00:06:13.105 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>His success is a testament to</i>
 <i>his intellect and grit,</i>

00:06:13.138 --> 00:06:16.674 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>but he got a lot of help from</i>
 <i>people in high places.</i>

00:06:16.708 --> 00:06:21.277 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>Of course, it also doesn't hurt</i>
 <i>that he comes from a noble</i>
 <i>family.</i>

00:06:25.013 --> 00:06:25.513 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hmph!

00:06:27.181 --> 00:06:29.616 position:69% line:89% align:start
[Screams]

00:06:31.384 --> 00:06:32.317 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:06:35.252 --> 00:06:37.288 position:24% line:89% align:start
So long, roaches.

00:06:40.290 --> 00:06:43.891 position:55% line:83% align:start
Yaeko, hold on
tight, like this.

00:06:44.258 --> 00:06:48.528 position:7% line:77% align:start
Now take us to full power. And
don't let your hand slow us
down.

00:06:48.562 --> 00:06:50.496 position:5% line:89% align:start
Time to catch up with Michelle.

00:06:52.297 --> 00:06:53.631 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Screams]

00:06:59.602 --> 00:07:01.036 position:5% line:89% align:start
They're charging us!

00:07:01.069 --> 00:07:02.237 position:52% line:83% align:start
Then we'll just
go through them!

00:07:06.607 --> 00:07:10.242 position:7% line:83% align:start
You...You're gonna fight them
from there?

00:07:13.177 --> 00:07:17.279 position:16% line:83% align:start
Just hold on, I'm coming
Michelle.

00:07:18.314 --> 00:07:19.281 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Growls]

00:07:21.249 --> 00:07:24.151 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) I've heard rumors</i>
 <i>that his family has in a way</i>
 <i>engineered itself to perfection.</i>

00:07:24.184 --> 00:07:26.119 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Supposedly for centuries,</i>

00:07:27.886 --> 00:07:30.589 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>members have picked spouses not</i>
 <i>for their wealth, connections,</i>
 <i>race, or nationality.</i>

00:07:30.622 --> 00:07:34.057 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>They've based their selection on</i>
 <i>three factors alone:</i>

00:07:34.090 --> 00:07:37.627 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Looks, talent, and resistance to</i>
 <i>disease.</i>

00:07:37.660 --> 00:07:42.363 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>In other words, his family has</i>
 <i>engaged in selective breeding.</i>

00:07:42.397 --> 00:07:49.000 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>For starters, they're working</i>
 <i>with the mightiest predator in</i>
 <i>the animal kingdom: humans.</i>

00:07:49.033 --> 00:07:54.504 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>With the endurance and lung</i>
 <i>capacity to run 42 kilometers an</i>
 <i>hour at full speed,</i>

00:07:54.537 --> 00:07:57.606 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>the throwing power that drove</i>
 <i>the mammoth to extinction,</i>

00:07:57.639 --> 00:08:01.509 position:10% line:83% align:start
the intelligence of a person
with an IQ of 186,

00:08:03.309 --> 00:08:08.179 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>an accelerated metabolism</i>
 <i>capable of immediate digestion</i>
 <i>and absorption of nutrients.</i>

00:08:08.647 --> 00:08:14.316 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>The ability to create any kind</i>
 <i>of military weapon, and use it</i>
 <i>like a master.</i>

00:08:18.486 --> 00:08:21.121 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Joseph) It's taken 600 years...</i>

00:08:22.288 --> 00:08:25.090 position:5% line:89% align:start
Behold the pinnacle of humanity!

00:08:26.291 --> 00:08:29.560 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Joseph) A human being created</i>
 <i>in the perfect image of God!</i>

00:08:33.328 --> 00:08:34.196 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:08:34.229 --> 00:08:34.730 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Gasps]

00:08:34.763 --> 00:08:39.032 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Yaeko) Wow...</i>

00:08:39.065 --> 00:08:41.134 position:5% line:89% align:start
We caught up already? [Gasps]

00:08:49.606 --> 00:08:51.707 position:5% line:89% align:start
They're getting close! [Groans]

00:09:01.347 --> 00:09:04.650 position:7% line:83% align:start
The Mosaic Organ procedure for
military combatants...

00:09:04.683 --> 00:09:08.285 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) depends on the</i>
 <i>individual's innate strength and</i>
 <i>abilities.</i>

00:09:08.318 --> 00:09:12.321 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>So there was never any doubt. We</i>
 <i>knew he'd be the strongest.</i>

00:09:14.122 --> 00:09:14.689 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:09:15.055 --> 00:09:15.590 position:35% line:89% align:start
[All] Huh?

00:09:18.325 --> 00:09:20.226 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) He is Rank 1.</i>

00:09:24.328 --> 00:09:25.563 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:09:31.333 --> 00:09:33.301 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) M.A.R.S. Ranking 1.</i>

00:09:36.369 --> 00:09:41.372 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Humanity in its</i>
 <i>ultimate form: Joseph G. Newton.</i>

00:09:44.408 --> 00:09:45.742 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hmph!

00:09:56.082 --> 00:09:57.116 position:27% line:89% align:start
It's about time.

00:09:57.684 --> 00:09:59.718 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Exhales]

00:10:04.187 --> 00:10:04.754 position:41% line:89% align:start
Joe...

00:10:06.222 --> 00:10:09.457 position:5% line:77% align:start
Wait, Michelle. Sit tight for a
moment, please. This will all be
over soon.

00:10:09.491 --> 00:10:10.425 position:47% line:5% align:start
 <i>Who is this guy?</i>

00:10:10.458 --> 00:10:12.794 position:10% line:89% align:start
I guarantee I can save you.

00:10:12.827 --> 00:10:16.729 position:10% line:83% align:start
Thanks, but no thanks. Even if
it means fighting Rank 1...

00:10:16.762 --> 00:10:20.599 position:7% line:77% align:start
My objective remains the same,
capture and deliver First and
Second.

00:10:20.632 --> 00:10:25.568 position:7% line:77% align:start
Wow, are you sure you want to
take me on? Because this isn't
exactly an even fight.

00:10:35.741 --> 00:10:36.609 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Surprised Noise]

00:10:39.143 --> 00:10:40.310 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hmph!

00:10:43.513 --> 00:10:44.780 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:10:47.082 --> 00:10:48.115 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:10:48.717 --> 00:10:52.151 position:13% line:83% align:start
What do you think? Can Joseph
take this guy down?

00:10:52.185 --> 00:10:54.654 position:5% line:83% align:start
A number of factors will
determine who will win.

00:10:55.153 --> 00:10:59.557 position:19% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) First, the</i>
 <i>terraformars. They're attacking</i>
 <i>them during the battle.</i>

00:10:59.590 --> 00:11:02.759 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) With his back to the</i>
 <i>roaches, Bao is at a</i>
 <i>disadvantage.</i>

00:11:04.260 --> 00:11:07.161 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Akari) Right, but these two are</i>
 <i>really swinging their swords.</i>

00:11:07.195 --> 00:11:10.197 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Akari) That puts Joseph at a</i>
 <i>disadvantage since his weapon's</i>
 <i>heavier.</i>

00:11:10.230 --> 00:11:12.265 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) And then there's each</i>
 <i>weapon's range.</i>

00:11:12.298 --> 00:11:15.700 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Joe's got the longer</i>
 <i>blade, so he wins there, but...</i>

00:11:15.734 --> 00:11:18.836 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Akari) Air resistance! Plus the</i>
 <i>laws of inertia.</i>

00:11:18.869 --> 00:11:21.738 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Akari) Since he's standing</i>
 <i>upwind, Bao has that advantage.</i>

00:11:21.771 --> 00:11:23.805 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:11:24.273 --> 00:11:24.873 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Gasps]

00:11:24.907 --> 00:11:26.374 position:16% line:89% align:start
He abandoned his sword?

00:11:26.707 --> 00:11:28.608 position:13% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Bao) That's an odd way to</i>
 <i>regroup.</i>

00:11:31.277 --> 00:11:32.511 position:24% line:89% align:start
You can't escape.

00:11:35.413 --> 00:11:36.614 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Inhales]

00:11:40.683 --> 00:11:44.452 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Sighs] And here I thought you'd
know to be more careful...

00:11:44.486 --> 00:11:45.386 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:11:45.419 --> 00:11:47.220 position:5% line:89% align:start
Or did you just forget?

00:11:47.253 --> 00:11:48.254 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Gasps]

00:11:50.355 --> 00:11:51.423 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:11:53.291 --> 00:11:56.293 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Joseph) Terraformars are quite</i>
 <i>particular about which victims</i>
 <i>they like to target.</i>

00:11:56.326 --> 00:12:00.429 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>They especially like the</i>
 <i>wounded. People on their own.</i>
 <i>Women.</i>

00:12:00.462 --> 00:12:02.564 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>And those with tools or weapons.</i>

00:12:03.231 --> 00:12:05.232 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:12:05.799 --> 00:12:11.770 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>This is bad, real bad. I need to</i>
 <i>use the serum to heal my wounds.</i>

00:12:11.803 --> 00:12:14.371 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>But how do I buy myself time to</i>
 <i>do that?</i>

00:12:15.239 --> 00:12:17.574 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Grunts] No, Michelle!

00:12:17.607 --> 00:12:18.508 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:12:19.675 --> 00:12:22.243 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Bao) If I kick First out of the</i>
 <i>vehicle...</i>

00:12:22.276 --> 00:12:23.744 position:21% line:5% align:start
 <i>That'll attract the</i>
 <i>terraformars.</i>

00:12:25.812 --> 00:12:27.179 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:12:27.212 --> 00:12:30.381 position:13% line:83% align:start
Asshole. What do you think
you're doing?

00:12:32.149 --> 00:12:33.450 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:12:33.851 --> 00:12:36.686 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hey, what were you thinking?

00:12:40.322 --> 00:12:41.155 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Gasps]

00:12:44.524 --> 00:12:47.860 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Grunting] How?

00:12:47.894 --> 00:12:49.595 position:24% line:89% align:start
How did I do that?

00:12:51.162 --> 00:12:53.463 position:7% line:77% align:start
If you're thinking about that
right when you're dying, you're
truly deranged.

00:12:55.164 --> 00:12:57.499 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Joseph) Could you be one of</i>
 <i>those hardshell types who can</i>
 <i>regenerate limbs?</i>

00:12:57.533 --> 00:13:01.301 position:13% line:77% align:start
Then again, your chance of
surviving this is more or less
nil.

00:13:01.335 --> 00:13:04.838 position:5% line:83% align:start
And if you do and you decide to
come after Michelle again...

00:13:04.871 --> 00:13:06.572 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'll chop you up into bloody
pulp!

00:13:06.606 --> 00:13:08.173 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:13:09.406 --> 00:13:10.774 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:13:15.277 --> 00:13:16.678 position:41% line:89% align:start
Huh...

00:13:16.712 --> 00:13:20.481 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Sighs] I can't regenerate from
this.

00:13:26.585 --> 00:13:27.452 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:13:28.686 --> 00:13:30.654 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:13:30.687 --> 00:13:31.388 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

