00:13:41.427 --> 00:13:42.895 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Joseph) I'm starting to get it!</i>

00:13:42.929 --> 00:13:43.896 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:13:45.464 --> 00:13:51.701 position:5% line:77% align:start
