00:14:59.377 --> 00:15:03.380 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Joseph) Her name was Marcia.</i>
 <i>She didn't have as much range as</i>
 <i>whoever's firing at us now</i> .

00:15:05.314 --> 00:15:08.917 position:10% line:83% align:start
