after we landed.

00:15:09.451 --> 00:15:13.854 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Joseph) On the first night they</i>
 <i>surrounded us. I had to make a</i>
 <i>hard choice.</i>

00:15:13.888 --> 00:15:16.355 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I knew I couldn't protect</i>
 <i>everyone,</i>

00:15:16.388 --> 00:15:20.958 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>so I used aggregation pheromones</i>
 <i>to lure a huge army of them to</i>
 <i>come after me.</i>

00:15:20.992 --> 00:15:23.827 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>To take care of the</i>
 <i>non-combatants in our squad,</i>

00:15:23.860 --> 00:15:27.262 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>I arranged their evacuation in</i>
 <i>an escape vehicle.</i>

00:15:27.295 --> 00:15:29.898 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>And I left Marcia and one other</i>
 <i>in charge.</i>

00:15:29.931 --> 00:15:34.600 position:5% line:77% align:start
