00:16:39.909 --> 00:16:43.946 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>It's funny, just a moment ago I</i>
 <i>was suspicious of this guy.</i>

00:16:43.979 --> 00:16:47.314 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Akari) So many have tried to</i>
 <i>betray us.</i>

00:16:47.347 --> 00:16:52.350 position:5% line:5% align:start
