00:17:18.101 --> 00:17:22.103 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yaeko, I'm glad you're safe.

00:17:22.137 --> 00:17:23.604 position:72% line:89% align:start
So am I.

00:17:24.005 --> 00:17:27.440 position:21% line:5% align:start
 <i>I'm glad too, truly.</i>

00:17:27.940 --> 00:17:30.342 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>(Joseph) When we use the serum</i>
 <i>to mutate and heal,</i>

00:17:30.375 --> 00:17:34.577 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>we destroy our human tissue and</i>
 <i>replace it with that of another</i>
 <i>organism.</i>

00:17:34.611 --> 00:17:37.113 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>There's a price to pay for this</i>
 <i>regeneration.</i>

00:17:37.147 --> 00:17:41.916 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>The serum damages in the long</i>
 <i>term, it shortens the human</i>
 <i>lifespan.</i>

00:17:41.949 --> 00:17:44.584 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Joseph) Michelle, what happened</i>
 <i>to the serum assigned to you?</i>

00:17:44.618 --> 00:17:45.518 position:30% line:89% align:start
