sharing a future with me.

00:18:30.413 --> 00:18:31.048 position:38% line:89% align:start
[Spits]

00:18:31.381 --> 00:18:31.781 position:72% line:89% align:start
[Grunts]

00:18:31.815 --> 00:18:32.849 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:18:33.382 --> 00:18:34.950 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Chuckles]

00:18:34.983 --> 00:18:37.518 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uhh.

