00:19:45.696 --> 00:19:48.531 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Kyo) And the Mosaic Organ</i>
 <i>Program?</i>

00:19:51.766 --> 00:19:56.569 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Michelle) Come on, Joe. You</i>
 <i>said the exact same thing to me</i>
 <i>like four days after we met.</i>

